OL,3,CMan arrested after years on run faces
OL,4,Cmore abuse charges
OL,6,FCheshire Police say an 80-year-old man
OL,7,Fwho was arrested after more than 27
OL,8,Fyears on the run is facing further
OL,9,Fcharges over alleged child sexual
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FRichard Burrows was arrested on
OL,13,FThursday 28 March at Heathrow Airport
OL,14,Fhaving returned to the UK from
OL,15,FThailand.
OL,17,FFollowing his arrest the 80-year-old
OL,18,Fappeared in Court on Tuesday 2 April
OL,19,Fwhere he was remanded in custody and
OL,20,Fis next set to appear at Chester Crown
OL,21,FCourt on Monday 5 August.
