OL,3,CMan arrested after years on run faces
OL,4,Cmore abuse charges
OL,6,FThe charges relate to allegations of
OL,7,Fabuse reported to have taken place
OL,8,Fwhile Mr Burrows worked as a carer at
OL,9,Fa children's home in Congleton,
OL,10,FCheshire, between 1969 and 1971 and in
OL,11,Fthe West Midlands between 1968 and
OL,12,F1995.
OL,14,FThe force said the majority of the
OL,15,Falleged offences in the West Midlands
OL,16,Frelated to local Scout groups where Mr
OL,17,FBurrows worked as a leader.
