OL,3,CMan arrested after years on run faces
OL,4,Cmore abuse charges
OL,6,FThey said the further 23 charges had
OL,7,Fbeen authorised by the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution ahead of Mr Burrows's
OL,9,Fappearance at Chester Crown Court
OL,10,Flater.They added that he was now
OL,11,Ffacing 78 counts of indecent assault,
OL,12,Fsix of a serious sexual offence, two
OL,13,Fof indecency with a child and three of
OL,14,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,16,FHe has also been charged with four
OL,17,Fcounts of possession of a false
OL,18,Fidentity document with intent.
